        <abstract>
            <p>Asks for London address of George King [Superintendent of Royal Botanic Garden, Calcutta], so he can ask about worm-castings sent by King from S. India. Has just received a splendid letter from John Scott on worms.</p> 
<p>Asks where he can buy <hi rend="italic">Dionaea</hi>.</p> 
